text: Proctocera quadriguttata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1914. It is known from Gabon, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, and Uganda.BioLib.cz - Proctocera quadriguttata.
